metadata.name: DALI
metadata.description:
Welcome to DALI, a collection of 1 out of 1 digital art pieces inspired by the surreal works of Salvador Dalí. 

Explore the dreamlike landscapes, melting clocks, and other surreal elements that capture the essence of Dalí's iconic style. 

Each DALI NFT is a unique and rare piece of art, authenticated and secured on the Ethereum blockchain for permanent ownership.
